Package org.apache.juneau.rest.client

Interface RestRequestCreated

public interface RestRequestCreated
Identify an HttpRequest that was created by a RestRequest.

Allows HTTP client code to get access to the underlying RestRequest if needed.

  • juneau-rest-client

  • Method Summary

    Modifier and Type Method Description
    RestRequest getRestRequest()
    Returns the RestRequest object that created the HttpRequest.

  • Method Details

    • getRestRequest

      RestRequest getRestRequest()
      Returns the RestRequest object that created the HttpRequest.
      Returns:
      The RestRequest object that created the HttpRequest.
